<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>
<div class="row mt-4 mb-5">
  <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2 surface-card">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-muted">Last updated <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-US", { year: "numeric", month: "long" }) %></p>
    <p>HavenNest collects only what's needed to run the service: your account details (username, email), the listings and reviews you create, and your wishlist. We don't sell your data to third parties.</p>
    <p>Listing images are stored with our media provider (Cloudinary). Location text you enter for a listing is sent to OpenStreetMap's Nominatim service to place it on the map.</p>
    <p>This is placeholder content for a demo project — replace it with real legal copy before taking HavenNest to production.</p>
  </div>
</div>
